1. Ono što *ukazuje* na to da je problem ozbiljan jeste veliki broj pritužbi. (What *indicates* that the problem is serious is the large number of complaints.)
2. Naučno istraživanje *ukazuje* da redovno vežbanje ima pozitivan uticaj na zdravlje. (Scientific research *suggests* that regular exercise has a positive impact on health.)
3. Učitelj je gestikulirao i *ukazao* prstom na tablu kako bi objasnio zadatke. (The teacher gestured and *pointed* at the board to explain the tasks.)
4. Smrtni slučajevi u proteklih nekoliko nedelja *ukazuju* na to da je potrebno ozbiljno shvatiti opasnost virusa. (The deaths in the past few weeks *indicate* that the danger of the virus needs to be taken seriously.)
5. Novi zakon *ukazuje* na to da će kazne za prekršaje biti rigoroznije. (The new law *suggests* that the fines for violations will be more severe.)
6. Kritike na račun uprave *ukazale* su na nedostatke u organizaciji. (The criticism of the management *pointed out* the shortcomings in organization.)
7. Zastava na vrhu zgrade *ukazuje* na to da se tu nalazi kancelarija državne uprave. (The flag on top of the building *indicates* that there is a government office there.)
8. Neadekvatna ishrana *ukazuje* na moguće probleme sa zdravljem. (Inadequate nutrition *points to* potential health problems.)
9. Stručnjaci *ukazuju* na važnost pravilne hidracije tokom fizičke aktivnosti. (Experts *emphasize* the importance of proper hydration during physical activity.)
10. Nedostatak podrške *ukazuje* na to da će ovaj projekat biti teško realizovati. (The lack of support *indicates* that this project will be difficult to carry out.)